<!-- Ã¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢Â HTML STRUCTURE Ã¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢ÂÃ¢â€¢Â -->
<div id="fx-ch-{{ sid }}">

  {%- comment -%} Hero secondary loader removed — site logo preloader only {%- endcomment -%}
  <div class="fxch-loading-{{ sid }} is-hidden" id="fxch-load-{{ sid }}" hidden aria-hidden="true" style="display:none!important"></div>

  <!-- Sticky 100vh viewport -->
  <div class="fxch-sticky-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-sticky-{{ sid }}">

    {%- comment -%}
      Page-level video lives in theme.liquid (.fx-site-bg) so it continues
      under before/after → FAQ → footer. Hero only adds sticky atmosphere.
    {%- endcomment -%}

    <!-- Electric light spill (CSS bloom only) -->
    <div class="fxch-portal-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-portal-{{ sid }}" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="fxch-portal__bloom"></div>
      <div class="fxch-portal__bloom fxch-portal__bloom--ring"></div>
      <div class="fxch-portal__bloom fxch-portal__bloom--core"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Three.js Canvas (transparent — portal shows through) -->
    <canvas class="fxch-canvas-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-canvas-{{ sid }}"></canvas>

    <!-- Atmospheric overlays — layered hierarchy -->
    <div class="fxch-atmo-{{ sid }}">
      <div class="fxch-fog-layer-{{ sid }}" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="fxch-glow-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-glow-{{ sid }}"></div>
      <div class="fxch-glow-mid-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-glow-mid-{{ sid }}"></div>
      <div class="fxch-glow-core-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-glow-core-{{ sid }}"></div>
      <div class="fxch-contact-shadow-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-shadow-{{ sid }}"></div>
      <div class="fxch-energy-pulse-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-pulse-{{ sid }}" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="fxch-reflect-{{ sid }}" id="fxch-ref-{{ sid }}"></div>
      <div class="fxch-vignette-{{ sid }}"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content panels -->
    <div class="fxch-panels-{{ sid }}">

      <!-- PANEL 0: Hero â€” stack: copy / product slot / CTA -->
      <div class="fxch-panel fxch-panel--hero" id="fxch-hero-{{ sid }}">
        <div class="fxch-hero-top">
          {%- if settings.logo_light != blank -%}
            {{ settings.logo_light | image_url: width: 240 | image_tag: class: 'fxch-eyebrow-logo', alt: shop.name }}
          {%- elsif settings.logo != blank -%}
            {{ settings.logo | image_url: width: 240 | image_tag: class: 'fxch-eyebrow-logo', alt: shop.name }}
          {%- else -%}
            <p class="fxch-eyebrow">FloorX</p>
          {%- endif -%}
          <h1 class="fxch-headline" id="fxch-headline-{{ sid }}">
            <span data-fxch-word>{{ h1 }}</span>
            <span data-fxch-word>{{ h2 }}</span>
            <span class="fxch-headline__outline" data-fxch-word>{{ h3 }}</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="fxch-product-slot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="fxch-hero-bottom">
          <p class="fxch-subheading">{{ sub }}</p>
          <div class="fxch-cta-row">
            <a href="{{ btn1_u }}" class="fx-btn fx-btn--primary fxch-btn fxch-btn--primary" id="fxch-btn1-{{ sid }}">
              {{ btn1_l }}
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 17 17" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M3.5 8.5h10M9.5 5l4 3.5-4 3.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PANEL 1: Problem (right) -->
      <div class="fxch-panel fxch-panel--problem" id="fxch-prob-{{ sid }}" aria-hidden="true">
        <p class="fxch-eyebrow">{{ 'floorx.hero.challenge' | t }}</p>
        <h2 class="fxch-section-title">{{ prob_t }}</h2>
        <ul class="fxch-list" role="list">
